<P>Informatics 141 / Computer Science 121: Course Reference<BR>
<strong>INFORMATION RETRIEVAL</strong></P>
<P> <B>Instructor:</B> <A HREF="http://www.ics.uci.edu/~kay/">David G. Kay</A>,
  5056 Donald Bren Hall (<code><A HREF="mailto:kay@uci.edu">kay@uci.edu</A></code>). TAs:
  Siva Thirunavukkarasu 
   (<code><A HREF="mailto:sthiruna@uci.edu">sthiruna@uci.edu</A></code>) and
   Shriti Raj
  (<code><A HREF="mailto:shritir@uci.edu">shritir@uci.edu</A></code>).</P>
<P><B>Quick links: </B><a href="http://nlp.stanford.edu/IR-book/pdf/irbookonlinereading.pdf">Textbook</a> <a href="http://www.ics.uci.edu/~kay/courses/i141/hw/index.html">Assignments</a>
