  in Informatics 141 / CS 121: <BR>
  </B>&mdash; If you do not have a UCInet ID,
  get one.  See <code><A HREF="http://activate.uci.edu/">http://activate.uci.edu/</A></code>. <BR>
  &mdash; If you prefer to read your electronic mail on an account other than your
  UCInet account, redirect your mail at <code><A HREF="http://www.oit.uci.edu/email/deliverypoint.html">http://www.oit.uci.edu/email/deliverypoint.html</A></code>.<BR>
