  &mdash; Go to <a href="http://checkmate.ics.uci.edu/">checkmate.ics.uci.edu</a>, log in with your UCInet ID, choose &quot;Course Listing&quot; and &quot;Winter 2015,&quot;click &quot;Go&quot; next to Informatics 141, and then click &quot;List me for this course.&quot; You'll submit most of your work electronically; this step is necessary to set that up. <br>
